-> kafka maintains set of client libraries for java
-> Include these libraries in your application to interact with kafka.

Types of API:
==============

-> Producer API : allow you to build producers
-> Consumer API : allow you to build Consumers
-> Streams API  : allow you to read from input topics, transform data and output to output topics.
-> Connect API  : allow you to build custom connectors which pull from or push to external system.
-> AdminClient API: manage and inspect higher level objects like topics and brokers.
